                <h1>Duke men&#039;s basketball awarded No. 2 seed in NCAA tournament following dazzling ACC title run</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/4e936fe4-9048-4745-a0d6-3e2e07c62e47.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;ACC&#x20;tournament&#x20;MVP&#x20;Luke&#x20;Kennard&#x20;has&#x20;been&#x20;remarkably&#x20;consistent&#x20;all&#x20;year,&#x20;averaging&#x20;20.1&#x20;points&#x20;per&#x20;game&#x20;and&#x20;20.0&#x20;during&#x20;the&#x20;conference&#x20;tournament.&amp;nbsp&#x3B;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>ACC tournament MVP Luke Kennard has been remarkably consistent all year, averaging 20.1 points per game and 20.0 during the conference tournament.&nbsp;</p>

